Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This property provides the new tenant with a great opportunity to locate in an easy accessible area in a functional, free-standing building.

Benefits of the building include:

* 928 sqm high clearance warehouse
* 262 sqm fitted out offices
* 25 sqm cold store (optional)
* Dual cross over for easy truck movements
* Multiple roller doors accessing warehouse
* Ready to occupy

For further information please contact exclusive agent David Corke via the links above.

Located approximately 30kms south east of the Brisbane CBD, the property provides excellent access to both the M1/Pacific Highway and the Logan Motorway. 

Features of the property include: 

-       662sqm Building area 
-	Modern high bay warehouse with great natural light 
-	Ground floor air-conditioned showroom 
-	Mezzanine storage and air-conditioned office 
-	Access via container height roller door 
-	Secured site with permitter fencing, electric gate and security patrol 

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agent from CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FUNCTIONAL FACILITY 1 MINUTE OFF M1 MOTORWAY

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
- 2000sqm clear span warehouse
- 100sqm ground floor
- Good concrete apron at front
- Close to M1 highway

Located 30km's south east of Brisbane at the junction of the M1 and Logan Motorway. Loganholme is a sought after industrial precinct, characterised by its proximity to the 3 major arterials on the south side of Brisbane. This area has experienced rapid growth in recent years as established areas such as Slacks Creek and Springwood reach capacity.
